name: Shell Ondina Oil 941

localDocs.name: Ondina 941 United Kingdom EN TDG V2.2 19-Jun-2018
Ondina 941 United Kingdom EN 140002340634 EHS V2.7 25-MAY-2023

marketing: Shell Ondina Oils are highly refined, non-stabilised, aromatic-free paraffinic or naphthenic white mineral oils complying with the stringent pharmacopoeia purity requirements. Ondina oils can be used in pharmaceutical, food packaging, cosmetic and other applications, where this high purity is required by legislation or important for the quality of the finished product. Shell Ondina Oil 941 is suitable for food packaging and other applications coming into contact with food meeting the requirements of Regulation (EU) No. 10/2011.
